{
 "file": "_STG07SP.bin",
 "source_size": 35116,
 "built_size": 37971,
 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x11cc",
   "jp_len": 81,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "{00}ゃ{00}か{00}ィ{00}Sぁあいうえか！ょれダチッツテ{01}デ、トドナ。ネハバ·パ々ェーフれ·{00}！中{01}Mななな、{00}{01}！上{00}M連とな、{00}{01}ぁ捕捉到了！是大天使号！！",
   "zh_hex": "150042001b004f001415161718191b0644496566676869016a026b6c6d036f707104720753087449040006c0011333333302000106b20013db313302000115efcded67e7d7e7baef97e7b6efa5e844e83fe833ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1238",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好、就这样从正面接近！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c702e7c5e7b9e7dae88aef3be862efceefd8ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1262",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "从正面……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e88aef3be862090905000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1287",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽说是叛逃舰、但终究是我军的机密舰、{00}不忍将其击沉。",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7ede7b6ef43e8c2e7d402e7dbe8e2e906e7b6efcce7e0e7b4e7e4e9bde7d40200e7b5eb59e84ae8cfe7cce98303000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12a8",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "首先、先向对方发出劝降。",
   "zh_hex": "15ef40ef8b02ef8befc1e7beefb1e870efbeebb6e9430300000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12d3",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……也罢、就请舰长随意吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c0eaef02e7c5e83ae7d4ef34e9a1ef3ce7d0000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12ec",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、我看多半是徒劳无功。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602efcce7f6e7e9eadee7b6eb02ec4ae7dce9b103000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1315",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x133c",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好久不见了、拉米亚斯舰长。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7e9dbe7b5e85ce7ba02e7c2e878e7d6e7c8e7d4ef3403000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x136d",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟要以这种形式相见、我深感遗憾。",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2cef2ae7f3e7b9e7d1ec67ea26e8b1e85c02efcceb0de87deba9ed6103000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13a0",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是啊。",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e7c3030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13c3",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿拉斯加的事、我也有所耳闻。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e7c2e7c8e854e7b4efb802efcce7c0e7cbe7fbee89ebac030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13d8",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……可是、还请您就此投降、再同军方高{00}层谈一次！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c4e7b602e7f7e83ae835e7c5e7cae948e94302e80be85de7e0efb1e81200ebc1eaf4efb6e864ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13f4",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我也会尽我所能、替您辩护！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7c0e7e2e8f2efcce7fbe7c602ea50e835eeb2e8e0ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1423",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "谢谢你……娜塔尔。",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b2e8b2e7b80909e7eae945e7e1030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1436",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可是、那种事我做不到。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b602e7b7e7d1efb8efcce81ce7b5e7d703000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x145f",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "舰长……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d4ef340909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1483",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "并不只是阿拉斯加那件事……",
   "zh_hex": "15e957e7b5ef32e7b6e7d2e7c2e7c8e854e7b7e991efb80909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1494",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们选择了对抗妄图扩大纷争的OZ",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe966eaaae7bae7bee912ecc6eb2dec1aefa5ecf8e852e7b4ed1ceeda000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14c2",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "因此、绝不投降、也绝不归队！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef33e7ca02e91ce7b5e948e94302e7c0e91ce7b5e947e7c9ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14fc",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊哈哈哈哈哈哈！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c3e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e8ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1508",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还想看您怎么做、真服了、舰长！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f7e7e6e7f6e835e7f2e7bde81c02e820e9f1e7ba02e7d4ef34ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1529",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要是说几句就能让人明白、这世上也就没{00}有纷争了。",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7b6e7edeaa5ebb9e7c5e7c6e7f9efb2ef39e80902e7b9e83cef4ce7c0e7c5e7d800e7cbecf8e852e7ba03000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1544",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正因为说不通、才会变成敌人、不是吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3bef33e7c1e7ede7b5ef5902e836e7e2e955e837e7e3efb202e7b5e7b6e8020500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1573",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿兹拉埃尔先生！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e856e7c2e96ae7e1ef8bef8def97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1599",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敌人就是非消灭不可的、那才是您的职责{00}吧、舰长？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e3efb2e7c5e7b6e8f0e928e8e1e7b5e7c4e7b402e7b7e836e7b6e835e7b4eda8eba600e7d002e7d4ef3405000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15ba",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "号称不沉的大天使号、这次就请您把它彻{00}底击沉吧。",
   "zh_hex": "15e833ea01e7b5e983e7b4efa5e844e83fe83302e7b9e864e7c5e83ae835e81be978ebc500e9b4e7cce983e7d0030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15ee",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15ff",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "全舰、MS发进！击沉大天使号！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb4e7d402efa7ef9ee870e892ef97e7cce983efa5e844e83fe833ef97ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x163b",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！这艘舰、也要到此为止了吗……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def97e7b9eb18e7d402e7c0ef2ae7d7e7cae7c1e869e7bae8020909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1674",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么能这样！{00}你这人也太不负责任了吧！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7c6e7b9e7da0600e7b8e7b9b4e7c0e86ae7b5e92ceba6e89ae7bae7d0060600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16b5",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "3点钟方向、发现新机影！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef60e822ebf9efb1efc102e870e82fef8ae7e4ea8eef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16de",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么、是敌人吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bd02e7b6e7e3efb2e802ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x170e",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "抱歉来迟了！我是OZ的杰克斯·马吉斯{00}特佐！",
   "zh_hex": "15e922e927d9ea10e7ba068be7b6ed1ceedae7b4e8ebe7d5e7c804e84fe7d9e7c800e7cfa306000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1728",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你便是主天使号的{00}娜塔尔·巴基露露中佐吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e8fae7b6e954e844e83fe833e7b400e7eae945e7e104e85be829e858e858c0a3e7d000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x173b",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我这就前去掩护贵队！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b9e7c5ef51e7ebec72e8e0e930e7c9ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x174c",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "上、诺茵！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef4c02e972e971ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x177c",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "明白、杰克斯！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef39e80902e8ebe7d5e7c8ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17aa",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "难道……是瑟拉吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e866e82a0909e7b6e8aae7c2e802060500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17d3",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "瑟拉？你这是在说谁呢？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8aae7c205e7b8e7b9e7b6ef29e7ede923e90705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1801",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "果然是瑟拉！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e871e7efe7b6e8aae7c2ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x180c",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可是、为什么！？那时候、你明明是被我{00}亲手……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b602e7c1e7dde7bdef9705e7b7ef2dea3902e7b8ef39ef39e7b6e7f1efcc00e894ef6609090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1841",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是瑟蕾因·伊克斯贝利、{00}不认识什么瑟拉。",
   "zh_hex": "158be7b6e8aae84cef3304e969e7d5e7c8e857e82e0200e7b5e8a0e92fe7dde7bde8aae7c2030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x185c",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你是不是认错人了？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b6e7b5e7b6e8a0e885efb2e7ba050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x188b",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bd0909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1892",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……瑟拉！你把我忘了吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8aae7c2ef97e7b8e81befccea4de7bae802ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18c2",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……抱歉、{00}这几年来的记忆、我都没有了。",
   "zh_hex": "150909e922e9270200e7b9eaa5e909d9e7b4e996eac6028be840e7d8e7cbe7ba0300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18f7",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1918",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们从前、或许曾经相识、可是……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe88aef5102e905e8a7ea2ae8b7e8b1e92f02e7c4e7b60909000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1933",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可惜、如今你我已是敌人。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e9c802e7f0efb9e7b8efccef3ae7b6e7e3efb203000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x193d",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要说恨意、啊……我想大概是没有的、不{00}过、还请你做好觉悟。",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7ede9beef3c02e7c30909efcce7e6efa5ec76e7b6e7d8e7cbe7b402e7b500ef3602e7f7e83ae7b8e81ce7c7e8aeea19030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1976",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19a4",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯？怎么了？",
   "zh_hex": "15e86505e7f2e7bde7ba05000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19d4",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是西格·韦德纳！机体出现了故障！",
   "zh_hex": "158be7b6e7f8e82404ebaee82ce88206e7e4bcafe82fe7baea09ebfc0600000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19eb",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我要后撤！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef2ae7fee90aef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a19",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……怎么、那家伙是没斗志了吗？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7f2e7bd02e7b7e7dfe7fde7b6e7d8e7ffea18e7bae802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a56",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "找到你了、卡缪！这一次、我定要将你击{00}倒！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9d2e7d7e7b8e7ba02e801e917ef97e7b9efb6e86402efcce867ef2ae84ae7b8e7cc00e848ef97ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a92",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是捷利特吗！？你居然还在执着于这种事{00}……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e7bce82ee7cfe8020605e7b8ea4ce7efe7f7ef29e9fce86de879e7b9e7d1a900090906060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1aa8",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "现在不是打这种仗的时候、这点你都不懂{00}吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e82fef29e7b5e7b6e7f5e7b9e7d1ea37e7b4ef2dea3902e7b9e822e7b8e840e7b5e8b000e802ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1aef",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是杰克斯·马吉斯吗……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e8ebe7d5e7c804e84fe7d9e7c8e802090906060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b1d",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "彼此承认对方是最强之敌、然后一战……",
   "zh_hex": "15efc9e7caea75e8a0e7beefb1e7b6e8c5e8ade7cde7e302e7efe7feefb6ef2809090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b2f",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这个提议、我可不能不接受！身为高达的{00}机师！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e828e821e8e302efcce7c4e7b5e7c6e7b5efcee8c8ef97e88de7c1e812ef2be7b400e7e4e96cef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b71",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那架MS的动作……难道说……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e99d1314e7b4ef30ef2f0909e866e82ae7ed0909060500000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b9f",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你这身手、我也是见过的、{00}赤色彗星先生！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b9e88dae028be7c0e7b6e85cef36e7b40200e9e9e89fe9b6b5b8b60600000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bda",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是强尼莱汀少佐吗！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e8ade896e846ed7cefacefbae802ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c01",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "从前还是一个阵营的、{00}这回却成了敌人……",
   "zh_hex": "15e88abae7f7e7b687e828eb48ed01e7b40200e7b98ceadfe837e7bae7e3b40909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c18",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你我二人、究竟谁的本事更高、能痛快地{00}一决高下、我可高兴得很！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8efccea13efb202e906ef2ce923e7b4efa6efb8e952e81202e7c6ea0be85fef6300efb6e8abe812ef4d02efcce7c4e812eabae80ae981ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c5d",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7de0909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c66",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "明明现在、根本没空{00}去理会一个机师啊……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef39ef39e82fef2902e9b8d2e7d8e93f00e7ebe872e7e287e828e7e4e96ce7c3090906060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cad",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！{00}有两下子嘛、杰克斯·马吉斯！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d09090600e7cbe97d89e886e93602e8ebe7d5e7c804e84fe7d9e7c8060600000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ce6",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "此刻、我感觉不到丝毫恐惧……{00}这场战斗、是我赢了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cae91f028be87de8aee7b5e7d7e8a3ea0aeb33ec6e090900e7b9e876ef28e7ff02e7b68be9cbe7ba06000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d04",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "纵然不动用多鲁基斯的全部力量、我也能{00}将你击倒、希罗·尤尔！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e6e7efe7b5ef30d8e7e9e8a2e829e7c8e7b4bbccdae851028be7c0e7c600e84ae7b8e7cce84802e87be7ec04ea5fe7e10606000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d49",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这下、您总该明白本舰的实力了吧。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9ef4d02e835e881e898ef39e809efa6e7d4e7b4e87fefb0e7bae7d003000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d60",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我这也是为你好、{00}奉劝你还是趁早投降吧。",
   "zh_hex": "158be7b9e7c0e7b6e7c1e7b8e7c70200eac1ebb6e7b8e7f7e7b6e9eae963e948e943e7d0030000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d9a",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dc7",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！剩下的就只能交给友军了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef97ea3aef4de7b4e7c5ef32e7c6e861e839e960e7e0e7baef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1de9",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿伽玛、全速后退！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e8e8e84502efb4e9dae7fee880ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e24",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊！喂、等等！！那艘战舰、可要跑掉了{00}啊！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c3ef97e8bd02e826e826ef97ef97e7b7eb18ef28e7d402e7c4ef2aeb6fe9d3e7ba00e7c3ef97050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e5b",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "凭那种损伤、它跑不了多远。",
   "zh_hex": "15ea49e7b7e7d1ea28e8f902e978eb6fe7b5e7bae7e9e94c03000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e70",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "再说、眼下还是以击破大天使号为先。",
   "zh_hex": "15e80be7ed02e90bef4de7f7e7b6e7f3e7ccef6defa5e844e83fe833e7c1ef8b030000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ea1",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ecf",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ef3",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "到此为止吧、拉米亚斯舰长。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d7e7cae7c1e869e7d002e7c2e878e7d6e7c8e7d4ef3403000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f01",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你若再继续抵抗下去、我们就只得击毁贵{00}舰了。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7e7e80be9d6e9ade96ee912ef4de7eb02efcce7bbe7c5ef32e80ae7cce97ce93000e7d4e7ba03000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f3d",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "娜塔尔……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7eae945e7e10909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f61",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我从前应该说过……{00}军队、是需要统制的。",
   "zh_hex": "158be88abae873e898e7edef36090900e7e0e7c902e7b6e92def2ae929e8dee7b4030000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f7d",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "大天使号的所作所为、无异于扰乱了这份{00}统制。",
   "zh_hex": "15efa5e844e83fe833e7b4e7fbef2fe7fbe7c102e7dceb32e879ebc7e976e7bae7b9ea2200e929e8de030000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f9a",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这是最后的通告、拉米亚斯舰长、请停止{00}抵抗、向我们投降。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7b6e8c5e7fee7b4ef59e8e502e7c2e878e7d6e7c8e7d4ef3402e83ae934e86900e96ee91202efc1efcce7bbe948e9430300000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fd7",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fe0",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不、娜塔尔、唯独这一点……我做不到。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b502e7eae945e7e102ea89e8eee7b9efb6e8220909efcce81ce7b5e7d7030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x200d",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2016",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……真遗憾。",
   "zh_hex": "150909e820eba9ed61030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2044",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "舰首！阳电子炮罗恩格林、展开！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d4ef40ef97eb72ead3e886e95ae7ece7eee824e9b702e989e7faef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x205a",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "目标、大天使号！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efd4e96f02efa5e844e83fe833ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x208b",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "永别了……玛琉·拉米亚斯",
   "zh_hex": "15e9bfe7e5e7ba0909e845ead2ef4be7c2e878e7d6e7c8000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20be",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20df",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "殖民地阴影中、出现新的舰影！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8a9ef38ef63eb22ea8eef4e02efbee82fef8ae7b4e7d4ea8eef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x210b",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2138",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "永恒号！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e9bfeb85e833ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x216b",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您没事吧、拉米亚斯舰长？",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7d8efb8e7d002e7c2e878e7d6e7c8e7d4ef34050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x219e",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "够了、请您住手吧！巴基露露小姐！",
   "zh_hex": "15e920e7ba02e83ae835e859ef66e7d0ef97e85be829e858e858e83ee921ef970000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21cb",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "基拉……大和……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e829e7c20909efa5e7d30909ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21f3",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们若执意要击沉大天使号、那么、就由{00}我……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbe7e7e9fcef3cef2ae7cce983efa5e844e83fe83302e7b7e7bd02e7c5e8a600efcc0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x220a",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "拉克丝·克莱因、来做你们的对手！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c2e7d5e8a304e7d5e846ef3302d9e81ce7b8e7bbe7b4e7beae06000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2247",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这下棘手了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9ef4ded79ef66e7ba09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2256",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟然不只是奥古、连PLANT的那位歌姬都{00}来助阵了……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ce7efe7b5ef32e7b6e82be84d02e86eeed4e81aea9ceed3eed6e7b4e7b7e834efd0ed56e84000d9ea23eb48e7ba09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2272",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、打算怎么应付他们？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7f5e889e7f2e7bde873e97ee80ce7bb05000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x229d",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我们不予理会。",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce7bbe7b5efb7e872e7e203000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22a9",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我判断、当前的不确定因素太多、此时暂{00}且后退、方为上策。",
   "zh_hex": "15efcceb29e98202ef53ef51e7b4e7b5e88ce867ef33ec86e86ae7e902e7caef2de9ff00e999e7fee88002efb1e7c1ef4cebe40300000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22e8",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啧……喂、等等、这是为什么！？我们明{00}明占着上风啊！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9fa0909e8bd02e826e82602e7b9e7b6e7c1e7dde7bdef9705efcce7bbef3900ef39eb51e86def4ceb75e7c3ef97ef970000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2308",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么一艘小小的战舰、究竟哪里算得上不{00}确定因素了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bdefb6eb18e83ee83ee7b4ef28e7d402e906ef2ce8ffef31e889e80aef4ce7b500e88ce867ef33ec86e7baef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x233c",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "若只有那艘叫永恒号的战舰、确实如理事{00}您所言。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e7ef32e7cbe7b7eb18e8c1e9bfeb85e833e7b4ef28e7d402e88ce87fe7f0e872efb800e835e7fbefd70300000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2379",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "诶……？",
   "zh_hex": "15eaf30909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x239b",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b60909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23c7",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2408",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嚯……不愧是你、{00}没想到、竟会被你看穿。",
   "zh_hex": "15e9dd0909e7b5ea08e7b6e7b80200e7d8e7e6e7d702ef2ce7e2e7f1e7b8e7f6ea7e03000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x244a",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "克鲁泽！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d5e8a2e984ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x246e",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我无意在此与你们交战……毕竟眼下我的{00}任务、是侦察。",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7dcef3cef29e7cae832e7b8e7bbe861ef280909ea2cef2ce90bef4defcce7b400e89ae94f02e7b6eeeaea8b03000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24aa",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24cd",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "作为证明、呵呵……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2fe7c1eba3ef3902ef3def3d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24da",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我就把本舰扣押的俘虏、归还给你们吧。",
   "zh_hex": "158be7c5e81bd2e7d4ee2aed60e7b4eadbebee02e947e7f7e839e7b8e7bbe7d0030000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x251b",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "扎夫特舰射出了逃生舱！",
   "zh_hex": "15e84be830e7cfe7d4ef65efbee7bae8c2ef8debebef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2554",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟特意送还个俘虏……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ce7cfef3ce9bae7f7e828eadbebee09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2560",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "总觉得、这事还挺勾人兴致的、您不觉得{00}吗、舰长？",
   "zh_hex": "15e881e8aee80a02e7b9efb8e7f7eb5cecb7efb2eabaea32e7b402e835e7b5e8aee80a00e80202e7d4ef34050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2595",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25d0",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……大、大天使号！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909be02bee844e83fe833060600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25dd",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "大天使号！救救我……！我……、我在这{00}里啊……！",
   "zh_hex": "15efa5e844e83fe833ef97e8cae8caefcc0909ef97efcc090902efccef29e7b900ef31e7c30909ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2612",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "芙蕾！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e9d7e84cef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2645",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！！是芙蕾·阿尔斯塔！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def97ef97e7b6e9d7e84cef4be7d2e7e1e7c8e945ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x267a",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是谁？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e9230500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26a1",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "她是已故的乔治·阿尔斯塔外务次官的女{00}儿。",
   "zh_hex": "15e88ee7b6ef3aea09e7b4edd0ea79ef4be7d2e7e1e7c8e945e8f7e94fe864ef92e7b4efad00eb7c03000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26d7",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哦……",
   "zh_hex": "15e91909090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2717",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "关、关键……！那个关键、就在我手里！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bb02e8bbeb710909ef97e7b7e828e8bbeb7102e7c5ef29efccef66ef31ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x272f",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "能终结这场战争的关键……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c6e8e2e868e7b9e876ef28e852e7b4e8bbeb7109090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2740",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所、所以……求你了、快救救我……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fb02e7fbe7f30909e93ae7b8e7ba02e85fe8cae8caefcc0909ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x277e",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……关键？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8bbeb71050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27ab",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "舰长！那个逃生舱、能回收吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d4ef34ef97e7b7e828e8c2ef8debeb02e7c6ef52e926e802ef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27de",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那个嘛……倒也并非做不到……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e828e9360909e848e7c0e957e8f0e81ce7b5e7d70909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x280e",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这不挺让人在意的吗、什么『终结战争的{00}关键』之类的话。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7b5eb5ce7f9efb2ef29ef3ce7b4e80202e7dde7bd0ce8e2e868ef28e852e7b400e8bbeb710de7cde841e7b4e81f0300000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x282f",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以呢、回收的事、就拜托您了。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f3e90702ef52e926e7b4efb802e7c5e91ae7f4e835e7ba030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x285f",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2868",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……遵命。",
   "zh_hex": "150909ec40e8530300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2899",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "目的虽然没能达成、但眼下嘛、就暂且算{00}了吧。",
   "zh_hex": "15efd4e7b4e8b8e7efe7d8e7c6ef2be83702e7dbe90bef4de93602e7c5e9ffe999e88900e7bae7d00300000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28bb",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、就请您后撤吧、舰长。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7c5e83ae835e7fee90ae7d002e7d4ef34030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28fc",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……全机、后撤！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909efb4e7e402e7fee90aef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x292f",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好久不见了、芙蕾·阿尔斯塔、你没事吧{00}？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7e9dbe7b5e85ce7ba02e9d7e84cef4be7d2e7e1e7c8e94502e7b8e7d8efb8e7d00005000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2961",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "巴、巴基露露中尉……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e85b02e85be829e858e858ef4eefc6090905000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x296f",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊……我、我……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c30909efcc02efcc09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2996",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、所谓的关键到底是什么？你真的拿{00}着吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7fbe92be7b4e8bbeb71e7d7e9b4e7b6e7dde7bd05e7b8e820e7b4e9a700e86de8020500000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29c9",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这、这个……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b902e7b9e82809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29ed",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哦、是张光盘啊……总觉得、看着还挺像{00}真的嘛？",
   "zh_hex": "15e91902e7b6eac5e83dec2fe7c30909e881e8aee80a02e7f6e86de7f7eb5ce8e900e820e7b4e936050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a23",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "克、克鲁泽队长……、那个戴面具的人…{00}…让我把它交出去……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d502e7d5e8a2e984e7c9ef34090902e7b7e828eb06e862ea14e7b4efb2090009e7f9efcce81be978e861efbee7eb09090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a60",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……能终结这场战争的关键、是吗……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909e7c6e8e2e868e7b9e876ef28e852e7b4e8bbeb7102e7b6e8020909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ab3",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "喂！后退是怎么回事！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bdef97e7fee880e7b6e7f2e7bdef52efb8ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ae0",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "方才那场战斗的经过、{00}贵官想必也清楚吧",
   "zh_hex": "15d0e836e7b7e876ef28e7ffe7b4e8b7ef360200e9308fe7e6e860e7c0e995ebd3e7d00000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2afc",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们的战力、不足以连扎夫特也一并与之{00}为敌。",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7b4ef28efb002e7b5ea1ee7f3e86ee84be830e7cfe7c0efb6e957e832e7cd00e7c1e7e3030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b32",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那种事、我也明白！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7d1efb802efcce7c0ef39e809ef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b42",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可就算要后退、也用不着一路退回地球吧{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7c5e889ef2ae7fee88002e7c0efb3e7b5e86defb6e8d2e880ef52ef63efd3e7d000ef970000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b5f",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "若是要重整态势、退去格里普斯或巴尔吉{00}、不也一样吗！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e7e7b6ef2ae8a1e9fee994e8fd02e880e7ebe824ef31e838e7c8e905e85be7e1e7d90002e7b5e7c087e7dae80206000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b9a",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好了好了……捷利特中尉、这可是必要之{00}举啊。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7e7bae7c7e7ba0909e7bce82ee7cfc08602e7b9e7c4e7b6e860ef2ae7cd00ea21e7c3030000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2bcf",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是你吗、下令夹着尾巴逃回去的！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e7b8e80202ef4de94eec5be86debc0e85be8c2ef52e7ebe7b4ef97050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c03",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这不叫逃跑、是为了凑齐必要的战力。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7b5e8c1e8c2eb6f02e7b6e7c1e7baecb1e924e860ef2ae7b4ef28efb0030000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c3a",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可是、就目前而言、我们能调动的战力、{00}再无其他了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b602e7c5efd4ef51e89cefd702efcce7bbe7c6e95cef30e7b4ef28efb00200e80be7dce8cfe80ce7ba09090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c70",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那方面已经有着落了、这都多亏了芙蕾·{00}阿尔斯塔小姐。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7efb1e862ef3ae8b7e7cbe86de92ae7ba02e7b9e840e7e9eab7e7bae9d7e84cef4b00e7d2e7e1e7c8e945e83ee9210300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ca7",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "芙蕾她？",
   "zh_hex": "15e9d7e84ce88e050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2cc9",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以呢、我们改日再来过。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f3e90702efcce7bbe9f0e98ae80befcfef360300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2cf4",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "喂……你！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bd0909e7b8ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d1a",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、先说好、这可是金主的命令。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302ef8be7ede7c702e7b9e7c4e7b6e902e954e7b4e853e94e030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d38",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "提坦斯若是要回绝我们的援助、那悉听尊{00}便。",
   "zh_hex": "15e821e843e7c8e7e7e7b6ef2aef52e91cefcce7bbe7b4e863ea2302e7b7ecd4e8d1eccd00e8fa0300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d50",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们就自己去追{00}那艘叫阿伽玛的战舰好了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbe7c5abe8c9e7ebe8dd00e7b7eb18e8c1e7d2e8e8e845e7b4ef28e7d4e7c7e7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d88",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2dab",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "无妨……准备工作转眼就能完成。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dce97f0909e87ae877eae4ef2fe9c2e90be7c5e7c6e87ee83703000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2dc0",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "迟早、也会请捷利特中尉尽兴一战的。",
   "zh_hex": "15ea10e96302e7c0e7e2e83ae7bce82ee7cfc086e8f2eaba87ef28e7b4030000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ddc",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "到那时、对手可就不止奥古了。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d7e7b7ef2d02e7beef66e7c4e7c5e7b5e869e82be84de7ba0300000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2df0",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "大天使号也好、永恒号也罢、还有……",
   "zh_hex": "15efa5e844e83fe833e7c0e7c702e9bfeb85e833e7c0eaef02e7f7e7cb090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e02",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……PLANT呢。",
   "zh_hex": "150909eed4e81aea9ceed3eed6e907030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e26",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿兹拉埃尔先生？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e856e7c2e96ae7e1ef8bef8d05000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e4c",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵呵呵……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3def3def3d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e6b",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "联邦那艘黑色长脚舰、撤退了吗……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ed1e7b7eb18ef3ee89fef34eb68e7d402e90ae880e7bae802090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e9e",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是。",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ea5",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来、他们已经撤回本部了。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcf02e80ce7bbef3ae8b7e90aef52efa6ef70e7ba030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ed2",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "原来如此……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e4efcfe7f0e7ca09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ed9",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来、他们已正确领会了那『关键』的含{00}义。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcf02e80ce7bbef3aef3be88cea20e7e2e7bae7b70ce8bbeb710de7b4ed3300e8ce030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f0b",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊？您是说……那『关键』吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c305e835e7b6e7ed0909e7b70ce8bbeb710de80205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f34",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "没什么……不过是我自己的事罢了。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d8e7dde7bd0909e7b5ef36e7b6efccefb5e8c9e7b4efb8eaefe7ba0300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f41",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵呵呵……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3def3def3d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f60",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "关于瑟蕾因·伊克斯贝利、我已向奥古本{00}部查问过了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bbe879e8aae84cef3304e969e7d5e7c8e857e82e028bef3a9de82be84dd200cceae9e997ef36e7ba0909000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f7a",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……这就是查问的结果、西格中尉。",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b9e7c5e7b6eae9e997e7b4e868e87102e7f8e824ef4eefc6030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2fa7",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2fb0",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这是……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7b60909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2fba",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "难道、她竟会是那样……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e866e82a02e88eef2ce7e2e7b6e7b7e7da090906000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2fe3",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这是从提坦斯那里得到的情报、虽然遗憾{00}、但极有可能属实。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7b6e88ae821e843e7c8e7b7ef31e80ae7d7e7b4e88be91302e8b8e7efeba9ed610002e7dbeacae7cbe7c4e7c6ea24e87f03000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x301c",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "瑟蕾因……、伊克斯贝利……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8aae84cef33090902e969e7d5e7c8e857e82e09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3027",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x302e",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d66",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您是说、要与主天使号交战吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7b6e7ed02ef2ae832e954e844e83fe833e861ef28e802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d76",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "大天使级的实力、想必您也十分清楚吧！{00}？",
   "zh_hex": "15efa5e844e83feaeee7b4e87fefb002e7e6e860e835e7c0ea4aefaee995ebd3e7d0ef9700050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7db1",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这我明白、娜塔尔……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9efccef39e80902e7eae945e7e109090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7dc4",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可是、我们不能就此停下脚步！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b602efcce7bbe7b5e7c6e7c5e7cae934ef4deb68ea93ef97000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e0f",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不要啊！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef2ae7c3ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e8a",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这一路走来的征战、辛苦了。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9efb6e8d2e890efcfe7b4ecd2ef2802ea58e9e6e7ba030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e97",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "衷心感谢你、将这条『宇宙世纪路线』一{00}路玩到了最后。",
   "zh_hex": "15edb3e82de87de8b2e7b802e84ae7b9e9d40ce8bee8bfe83ceb99e8d2e9160defb600e8d2e970e7d7e7bae8c5e7fe03000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7eb7",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、隆德·贝尔队的征战、就此暂告一{00}段落……",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7b4ecd2ef2802e7c5e7cae9ffe8e5efb600ea6be92a0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7ed6",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但游戏本身仍可继续、往后也愿你尽情游{00}玩下去。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e911e7fee7c0e961e7b8e8f2e88bea9400e970ef4de7eb030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7efb",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "此外、为通关本路线的你、还准备了一关{00}特别关卡。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cae8f702e7c1ef59e8bbefa6e8d2e916e7b4e7b802e7f7e87ae877e7baefb6e8bb00e7cfe7e5e8bbe801030000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7f22",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那便是与另行作战至今的大天使队进行的{00}特别演习。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e8fae7b6e832e99befd6ef2fef28e897efb9e7b4efa5e844e83fe7c9e892efd6e7b400e7cfe7e5ea2feab6030000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7f43",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "与他们一战、检验一下你亲手培养的部队{00}究竟有多强、也未尝不可。",
   "zh_hex": "15e832e80ce7bbefb6ef2802ee40ea99efb6ef4de7b8e894ef66edfeec0be7b4ef70e7c900e906ef2ce7cbe7e9e8ad02e7c0e8b4eccfe7b5e7c403000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7f68",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特别演习』、便能与{00}他们一决高下。",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29abe8a6e7beef28c0e966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d02e8fae7c6e83200e80ce7bb87e8abe8128903000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7f8d",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、就请尽情享受『SD高达G{00}世代DS』、",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd02e7c5e83ae8f2e88bec06e8c80c1411e812ef2beed100e83ce8e711140d0200000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7fb1",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也愿你慢慢品味、尽兴玩到最后。",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0e961e7b8e979e979eae1ed3602e8f2eabae970e7d7e8c5e7fe030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x802a",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一路走来、能陪着我这样不可靠的舰长、{00}真是谢谢你。",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e8d2e890efcf02e7c6ef42e86defcce7b9e7dae7b5e7c4e8c7e7b4e7d4ef340200e820e7b6e8b2e8b2e7b8030000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8049",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条「平成高达路线」、{00}就到此告一段落了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d4e9c3e887e837e812ef2be8d2e916e9c40200e7c5e7d7e7cae8e587ea6be92ae7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8067",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、虽说我们预防者的战斗已经结束…{00}…",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e8b8e7edefcce7bbea5ae968ef6ee7b4ef28e7ffef3ae8b7e868e895090009000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8081",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "游戏本身仍可继续哦、今后也请继续尽情{00}游玩下去。",
   "zh_hex": "15ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ade91902efb9e7fee7c0e83ae9d6e9ade8f2e88b00ea94e970ef4de7eb03000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x80a7",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为一路玩到最后的你、我们也准备了全新{00}的关卡哦。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1efb6e8d2e970e7d7e8c5e7fee7b4e7b802efcce7bbe7c0e87ae877e7baefb4ef8a00e7b4e8bbe801e9190300000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x80cb",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是与我们各自作战、一直在和提坦斯、{00}新吉翁交手的……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e8328be7bbe819abef2fef280287e875ef29e7d3e821e843e7c80200ef8ae7d9ee88e861aee7b40909000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x80e6",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……与隆德·贝尔队进行的特别演习哦。",
   "zh_hex": "150909e832ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e892efd6e7b4e7cfe7e5ea2feab6e919030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x80f9",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特别演习』、就能和{00}他们交战了哦。",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d02e7c5e7c6e7d300e80ce7bbe861ef28e7bae9190300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x811f",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请一定要挑战看看哦。",
   "zh_hex": "15e83aefb6e867ef2aeae7ef28e7f6e7f6e91903000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x812d",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、就请尽情享受『SD高达G{00}世代DS』、",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd02e7c5e83ae8f2e88bec06e8c80c1411e812ef2beed100e83ce8e711140d0200000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8151",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "「自由对战的战火！全速冲锋吧、大天使{00}号！！」",
   "zh_hex": "15e9c3abe8a6e7beef28e7b4ef28e8da06bbe9dae95ee967e7d002bee844e83f00e8330606e9c4000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x81d2",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是主天使号舰长、娜塔尔·巴基露露中{00}佐。",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e954e844e83fe833e7d4ef3402e7eae945e7e1ef4be85be829e858e858ef4e00efba030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x81e2",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "首先、请允许我向你一路以来出色的指挥{00}、致以敬意。",
   "zh_hex": "15ef40b802e83aecade8a78b9de7b887e8d2e7f3d9afe89fe7b4e8c0e9490002ea32e7f3ee38ef3c0300000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8204",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多亏有你的全力协助、我们才终于得以一{00}战到底。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e9eab7e7cbe7b8e7b4efb4efb0e8f6ea2302efcce7bbe836e8e2e879e80ae7f3efb600ef28e7d7e9b4030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8226",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『对手路线』、到此就结束了。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce7beef66e8d2e9160d02e7d7e7cae7c5e868e895e7ba030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x823c",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、虽说我们主天使队的战斗已经告终{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e8b8e7edefcce7bbe954e844e83fe7c9e7b4ef28e7ffef3ae8b7e8e5e8e2000909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8255",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但游戏本身仍可继续、往后也愿你尽情游{00}玩下去。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e911e7fee7c0e961e7b8e8f2e88bea9400e970ef4de7eb0300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8279",
   "jp_len": 43,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "自由对战今后仍可继续、此外、只要选择{00}『特别演习』……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb5e8a6e7beef28efb9e7feeab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e7cae8f702ef32ef2ae966eaaa000ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x82a4",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "便能与隆德·贝尔、{00}预防者进行联合演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e8fae7c6e832ed16e82c04e857e7e10200ea5ae968ade8929fef2ea0ea2feab600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x82c2",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我相信、以你的本事、与他们一战、也定{00}能取得胜利。",
   "zh_hex": "158be8b1e90f02e7f3e7b8e7b4d2a902e832e80ce7bb87ef2802e7c0e86700e7c6e987e80ae8dbe82e0300000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x82e7",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、就请尽情享受『SD高达G{00}世代DS』、",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd02e7c5e83ae8f2e88bec06e8c80c1411e812ef2beed100e83ce8e711140d0200000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x830b",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后、也祝你奋战顺利。",
   "zh_hex": "15a2e7fe02e7c0ed97e7b8ef46ef28eab4e82e0300000000"
  }
 ]
}
